                "invention-title": [
                    "Rapid, safe and efficient hydrogen production system and hydrogen production method",
                    "一种快速安全高效制氢系统及制氢方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a rapid, safe and efficient hydrogen production system and a hydrogen production method, and solves the problems of long hydrogen energy raw material production process time, high energy consumption and difficulty in rapid hydrogen production and direct application of existing hydrogen production equipment. According to the technical scheme, a conical steam chamber is arranged in a high-temperature steam generator, an annular combustion chamber is arranged on the periphery, a double-layer gas storage chamber is arranged on the top, and the top of the gas storage chamber communicates with a high-temperature dryer through a conveying pipe; the annular combustion chamber is connected with an auxiliary combustor and a hydrogen combustor; and the hydrogen production catalytic reactor is connected with the condensation gas-liquid separator, the hydrogen burner, the hydrogen purification device and the hydrogen collector. According to the hydrogen production method, the prepared hydrogen can be used for providing high-temperature hot flue gas for heat supply, hydrogen production raw materials can be rapidly heated and gasified, hydrogen energy fuel can be prepared through catalytic reaction, the hydrogen energy fuel can be prepared instantly and can be purified and applied to use terminals, and high efficiency and energy conservation are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种快速安全高效制氢系统及制氢方法，解决了现有制氢设备制取氢能原料过程时间长，消耗能源多，难以快速制氢直接应用的问题。技术方案是：高温蒸汽生成器内部设置有圆锥形蒸气室，外围设置环状燃烧室，顶部设置有双层储气室，储气室顶部通过所述输送管连通高温干燥器；环状燃烧室连接有辅助燃烧器和氢气燃烧器；制氢催化反应器连接冷凝气液分离器、氢气燃烧器、氢气提纯装置和氢气收集器。制氢方法能够利用制取的氢气提供高温热烟气供热，其能够快速加热气化制氢原料，经催化反应制取氢能燃料，即时制备，并可提纯应用到使用终端，高效节能。"
                }
            ]
        }
